N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15 ยง 68.9 - Prior slow-moving emblems

State Regulations
A slow-moving vehicle emblem which was manufactured prior
to September 1, 1977, and which met the standards of this Part on the date of
manufacture may be sold and used in this State. Notes

comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
